text: Erechthias externella is a species of moth in the family Tineidae. It was described by Francis Walker in 1864. This species is endemic to New Zealand. ==References== ==External links== *Image of type specimen of Erechthias externella Category:Moths described in 1864 Category:Erechthiinae Category:Moths of New Zealand Category:Endemic fauna of New Zealand Category:Taxa named by Francis Walker
